# Math Problem Templates

HTML templates for solving Trigonometry and Compound Interest problems with visual step-by-step solutions.

## 📁 Files

| Template | Problem 1 | Problem 2 |
|----------|-----------|-----------|
| **Trigonometry** | [`Prob1-Trigonometry.html`](Prob1-Trigonometry.html) | [`Prob2-Trigonometry.html`](Prob2-Trigonometry.html) |
| **Compound Interest** | [`prob1-CI.html`](prob1-CI.html) | [`prob2-CI.html`](prob2-CI.html) |

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/math-problem-templates.git
cd math-problem-templates
# Open any HTML file in your browser

✨ Features
Visual step-by-step solutions

Color-coded mathematical notation

Interactive diagrams and layouts

No dependencies - pure HTML/CSS

🎯 Problems Solved
Trigonometry
Problem 1: 8-15-17 Pythagorean triplet → Sec C + Cot A = 5/3

Problem 2: 20-21-29 Pythagorean triplet → Sec C + Cot A = 7/3

Compound Interest
Problem 1: ₹8000 → ₹9261 in 3 years (Rate = 5%)

Problem 2: ₹5000 → ₹6050 in 2 years (Rate = 10%)


🛠️ Customization
Update existing templates by:

Changing numbers and variables

Modifying calculation steps

Keeping original CSS structure

⭐ Star this repo if you find it helpful!
